{"tid":1486171,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"關於嘉年華心態參與抗爭","createTime":"2019-08-18T19:21:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T12:31:22.000Z","uid":173326,"like":67,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"94625f431cad5e01c054faf33fb04f48917e4cee","tid":1486171,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T19:21:22.000Z","msg":"首先要明白唔係人人都抱住背水一戰、慷慨就義嘅心態參加抗爭<br />\n<br />\n現場見到大型和平嘅集會遊行，的確有各種唔同嘅同路人，<br />\n有人以身犯險還擊，有人奮不顧身去救人，有人熱愛音樂唱歌仔，有人怕熱開風扇仔、有人怕濕身開遮、有人怕犯法唔敢行馬路、有人想拍拖攬住女遊行、有人想reu同班朋友嘻嘻哈哈。。。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">大家都係向同一個方向前進，唔好在意同路人付出左啲乜，因為人人價值觀唔同，唔應該互相比較。<br />\n各位只需要問自己可以仲做啲乜，做人但求問心無愧。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"6b6a93932fe4e0897f68eca68539633006362252","tid":1486171,"uid":202577,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T19:22:41.000Z","msg":"無咁危險嘅情況係可以"},{"pid":"75a64591521868e9f110c35c911ff6e6bd1ae5cc","tid":1486171,"uid":228827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T19:23:22.000Z","msg":"同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e49908b8fe26778ceefe27703d646f408db230f2","tid":1486171,"uid":241458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T19:24:03.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">緊急</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n有人諗住聽朝0715塞鐵，好可能會spin走咗車長罷工嘅事，希望深水埗手足聽朝去勸下佢地<br />\n<br />\n佢地個group block咗我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/mtrisdangerous\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmtrisdangerous&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSsh6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=1911721e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/mtrisdangerous</a>"},{"pid":"cfa710184db6c3445314e922d009f34c48d975a5","tid":1486171,"uid":173326,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T19:25:44.000Z","msg":"利申埋先：我唔鼓勵亂世情侶行為，亦相當葡萄去現場拍拖嘅人，但我唔認為佢地有錯"},{"pid":"dd446727317e3d57981902a32e4d5347b88b7610","tid":1486171,"